# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Platform
- Target Runtime: Java 17+ (LTS)
- Deployment: Docker / Kubernetes
- Development OS: macOS / Linux / Windows

## Language & Frameworks
- Language: Java 17+
- Framework: Spring Boot 3.x
- Build Tool: Gradle (Kotlin DSL preferred)

## Architecture Components
- **API Style**: RESTful API
- **Architecture Pattern**: Hexagonal / Layered Architecture
- **Microservices Support**: Spring Cloud (if applicable)

## Data & Persistence
- **Primary Database**: PostgreSQL (Relational Data)
- **Cache & Session**: Redis (Lettuce/Redisson) - See [303-spring-redis-lettuce-redisson-rules.mdc](303-spring-redis-lettuce-redisson-rules.mdc)
- **Messaging / Event Streaming**: Apache Kafka - See [304-kafka-data-pipeline-rules.mdc](304-kafka-data-pipeline-rules.mdc)

## Key Libraries & Tools
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA / Hibernate
- **Validation**: Hibernate Validator
- **Testing**: JUnit 5, Mockito, Testcontainers
- **Docs**: SpringDoc OpenAPI (Swagger)

